I've made these muffins several times now and they have been consistently excellent. I tried a previous reviewer's recommendations for "healthier" muffins with decent results but my preferred version balancing taste with nutrition is: sub soy milk + lemon juice for buttermilk; use w.w. pastry flour instead of white; reduce fat by one quarter but don't replace with mashed banana or applesauce (compromises the fine texture). Add 1 tsp vanilla and use 3/4 c wild blueberries instead of currants.

